name: Aiport Shops
query:
SELECT 
    tabShop.name as "ID:Link/Shop:200",
    tabShop.`size` as "Size:Data:100", 
    tabShop.airport as "Airport:Data:200", 
    tabShop.`number` as "Number:Data/Shop:200", 
    tabShop.occupied as "Occupied:Check:100", 
    tabShop.available_to_lease as "Available:Check:100"
FROM tabShop;
